// frontend/src/pages/admin/BranchesManagement.jsx import React, { useState } from 'react'; import './AdminPages.css'; const BranchesManagement = () => { const [branches, setBranches] = useState([ { id: 1, name: 'غازي مول', location: 'الرياض', manager: 'أحمد محمد', gamesCount: 8, status: 'نشط', revenue: 15200 }, { id: 2, name: 'سكوير مول', location: 'الرياض', manager: 'سعود أحمد', gamesCount: 8, status: 'نشط', revenue: 12800 }, { id: 3, name: 'زمزم مول', location: 'الرياض', manager: 'فهد راشد', gamesCount: 6, status: 'نشط', revenue: 9800 }, { id: 4, name: 'نادي اكتوبر', location: 'الرياض', manager: 'نواف خالد', gamesCount: 5, status: 'نشط', revenue: 7600 }, { id: 5, name: 'نادي الجزيرة', location: 'الرياض', manager: 'تركي محمد', gamesCount: 5, status: 'غير نشط', revenue: 0 }, ]); const [showAddModal, setShowAddModal] = useState(false); const [newBranch, setNewBranch] = useState({ name: '', location: 'الرياض', manager: '', status: 'نشط' }); const handleAddBranch = () => { const newBranchData = { id: branches.length + 1, ...newBranch, gamesCount: 0, revenue: 0 }; setBranches([...branches, newBranchData]); setShowAddModal(false); setNewBranch({ name: '', location: 'الرياض', manager: '', status: 'نشط' }); }; return (
